verses.text_plain: Now these are the generations of Esau, who is Edom.
verses.verse_html: 1Now these are the generations of Esau, who is Edom.

verses.text_plain: Esau took his wives of the daughters of Canaan; Adah the daughter of Elon the Hittite, and Aholibamah the daughter of Anah the daughter of Zibeon the Hivite;
verses.verse_html: 2Esau took his wives of the daughters of Canaan; Adah the daughter of Elon the Hittite, and Aholibamah the daughter of Anah the daughter of Zibeon the Hivite;

verses.text_plain: And Bashemath Ishmael’s daughter, sister of Nebajoth.
verses.verse_html:
3And Bashemath Ishmael’s daughter, sister of Nebajoth. ▼
▼ Bashemath: or, Mahalath

verses.text_plain: And Adah bare to Esau Eliphaz; and Bashemath bare Reuel;
verses.verse_html: 4And Adah bare to Esau Eliphaz; and Bashemath bare Reuel;

verses.text_plain: And Aholibamah bare Jeush, and Jaalam, and Korah: these are the sons of Esau, which were born unto him in the land of Canaan.
verses.verse_html: 5And Aholibamah bare Jeush, and Jaalam, and Korah: these are the sons of Esau, which were born unto him in the land of Canaan.

verses.text_plain: And Esau took his wives, and his sons, and his daughters, and all the persons of his house, and his cattle, and all his beasts, and all his substance, which he had got in the land of Canaan; and went into the country from the face of his brother Jacob.
verses.verse_html:
6And Esau took his wives, and his sons, and his daughters, and all the persons of his house, and his cattle, and all his beasts, and all his substance, which he had got in the land of Canaan; and went into the country from the face of his brother Jacob. ▼
▼ persons: Heb. souls

verses.text_plain: For their riches were more than that they might dwell together; and the land wherein they were strangers could not bear them because of their cattle.
verses.verse_html: 7For their riches were more than that they might dwell together; and the land wherein they were strangers could not bear them because of their cattle.

verses.text_plain: Thus dwelt Esau in mount Seir: Esau is Edom.
verses.verse_html: 8Thus dwelt Esau in mount Seir: Esau is Edom.

verses.text_plain: And these are the generations of Esau the father of the Edomites in mount Seir:
verses.verse_html:
9And these are the generations of Esau the father of the Edomites in mount Seir: ▼
▼ the Edomites: Heb. Edom

footnotes.body_html: ▼ the Edomites: Heb. Edom

verses.text_plain: These are the names of Esau’s sons; Eliphaz the son of Adah the wife of Esau, Reuel the son of Bashemath the wife of Esau.
verses.verse_html: 10These are the names of Esau’s sons; Eliphaz the son of Adah the wife of Esau, Reuel the son of Bashemath the wife of Esau.

verses.text_plain: And the sons of Eliphaz were Teman, Omar, Zepho, and Gatam, and Kenaz.
verses.verse_html:
11And the sons of Eliphaz were Teman, Omar, Zepho, and Gatam, and Kenaz. ▼
▼ Zepho: or, Zephi

verses.text_plain: And Timna was concubine to Eliphaz Esau’s son; and she bare to Eliphaz Amalek: these were the sons of Adah Esau’s wife.
verses.verse_html: 12And Timna was concubine to Eliphaz Esau’s son; and she bare to Eliphaz Amalek: these were the sons of Adah Esau’s wife.

verses.text_plain: And these are the sons of Reuel; Nahath, and Zerah, Shammah, and Mizzah: these were the sons of Bashemath Esau’s wife.
verses.verse_html: 13And these are the sons of Reuel; Nahath, and Zerah, Shammah, and Mizzah: these were the sons of Bashemath Esau’s wife.

verses.text_plain: And these were the sons of Aholibamah, the daughter of Anah the daughter of Zibeon, Esau’s wife: and she bare to Esau Jeush, and Jaalam, and Korah.
verses.verse_html: 14And these were the sons of Aholibamah, the daughter of Anah the daughter of Zibeon, Esau’s wife: and she bare to Esau Jeush, and Jaalam, and Korah.

verses.text_plain: These were dukes of the sons of Esau: the sons of Eliphaz the firstborn son of Esau; duke Teman, duke Omar, duke Zepho, duke Kenaz,
verses.verse_html: 15These were dukes of the sons of Esau: the sons of Eliphaz the firstborn son of Esau; duke Teman, duke Omar, duke Zepho, duke Kenaz,

verses.text_plain: Duke Korah, duke Gatam, and duke Amalek: these are the dukes that came of Eliphaz in the land of Edom; these were the sons of Adah.
verses.verse_html: 16Duke Korah, duke Gatam, and duke Amalek: these are the dukes that came of Eliphaz in the land of Edom; these were the sons of Adah.

verses.text_plain: And these are the sons of Reuel Esau’s son; duke Nahath, duke Zerah, duke Shammah, duke Mizzah: these are the dukes that came of Reuel in the land of Edom; these are the sons of Bashemath Esau’s wife.
verses.verse_html: 17And these are the sons of Reuel Esau’s son; duke Nahath, duke Zerah, duke Shammah, duke Mizzah: these are the dukes that came of Reuel in the land of Edom; these are the sons of Bashemath Esau’s wife.

verses.text_plain: And these are the sons of Aholibamah Esau’s wife; duke Jeush, duke Jaalam, duke Korah: these were the dukes that came of Aholibamah the daughter of Anah, Esau’s wife.
verses.verse_html: 18And these are the sons of Aholibamah Esau’s wife; duke Jeush, duke Jaalam, duke Korah: these were the dukes that came of Aholibamah the daughter of Anah, Esau’s wife.

verses.text_plain: These are the sons of Esau, who is Edom, and these are their dukes.
verses.verse_html: 19These are the sons of Esau, who is Edom, and these are their dukes.

verses.text_plain: These are the sons of Seir the Horite, who inhabited the land; Lotan, and Shobal, and Zibeon, and Anah,
verses.verse_html: 20These are the sons of Seir the Horite, who inhabited the land; Lotan, and Shobal, and Zibeon, and Anah,

verses.text_plain: And Dishon, and Ezer, and Dishan: these are the dukes of the Horites, the children of Seir in the land of Edom.
verses.verse_html: 21And Dishon, and Ezer, and Dishan: these are the dukes of the Horites, the children of Seir in the land of Edom.

verses.text_plain: And the children of Lotan were Hori and Hemam; and Lotan’s sister was Timna.
verses.verse_html:
22And the children of Lotan were Hori and Hemam; and Lotan’s sister was Timna. ▼
▼ Hemam: or, Homam

verses.text_plain: And the children of Shobal were these; Alvan, and Manahath, and Ebal, Shepho, and Onam.
verses.verse_html:
23And the children of Shobal were these; Alvan, and Manahath, and Ebal, Shepho, and Onam. ▼
▼ Alvan: or, Alian
 , ▼
▼ Shepho: or, Shephi

verses.text_plain: And these are the children of Zibeon; both Ajah, and Anah: this was that Anah that found the mules in the wilderness, as he fed the asses of Zibeon his father.
verses.verse_html: 24And these are the children of Zibeon; both Ajah, and Anah: this was that Anah that found the mules in the wilderness, as he fed the asses of Zibeon his father.

verses.text_plain: And the children of Anah were these; Dishon, and Aholibamah the daughter of Anah.
verses.verse_html: 25And the children of Anah were these; Dishon, and Aholibamah the daughter of Anah.

verses.text_plain: And these are the children of Dishon; Hemdan, and Eshban, and Ithran, and Cheran.
verses.verse_html:
26And these are the children of Dishon; Hemdan, and Eshban, and Ithran, and Cheran. ▼
▼ Hemdan: or, Amram

verses.text_plain: The children of Ezer are these; Bilhan, and Zaavan, and Akan.
verses.verse_html:
27The children of Ezer are these; Bilhan, and Zaavan, and Akan. ▼
▼ Akan: or, Jakan

verses.text_plain: The children of Dishan are these; Uz, and Aran.
verses.verse_html: 28The children of Dishan are these; Uz, and Aran.

verses.text_plain: These are the dukes that came of the Horites; duke Lotan, duke Shobal, duke Zibeon, duke Anah,
verses.verse_html: 29These are the dukes that came of the Horites; duke Lotan, duke Shobal, duke Zibeon, duke Anah,

verses.text_plain: Duke Dishon, duke Ezer, duke Dishan: these are the dukes that came of Hori, among their dukes in the land of Seir.
verses.verse_html: 30Duke Dishon, duke Ezer, duke Dishan: these are the dukes that came of Hori, among their dukes in the land of Seir.

verses.text_plain: And these are the kings that reigned in the land of Edom, before there reigned any king over the children of Israel.
verses.verse_html: 31And these are the kings that reigned in the land of Edom, before there reigned any king over the children of Israel.

verses.text_plain: And Bela the son of Beor reigned in Edom: and the name of his city was Dinhabah.
verses.verse_html: 32And Bela the son of Beor reigned in Edom: and the name of his city was Dinhabah.

verses.text_plain: And Bela died, and Jobab the son of Zerah of Bozrah reigned in his stead.
verses.verse_html: 33And Bela died, and Jobab the son of Zerah of Bozrah reigned in his stead.

verses.text_plain: And Jobab died, and Husham of the land of Temani reigned in his stead.
verses.verse_html: 34And Jobab died, and Husham of the land of Temani reigned in his stead.

verses.text_plain: And Husham died, and Hadad the son of Bedad, who smote Midian in the field of Moab, reigned in his stead: and the name of his city was Avith.
verses.verse_html: 35And Husham died, and Hadad the son of Bedad, who smote Midian in the field of Moab, reigned in his stead: and the name of his city was Avith.

tokens.text: in his stead: and the name

verses.text_plain: And Hadad died, and Samlah of Masrekah reigned in his stead.
verses.verse_html: 36And Hadad died, and Samlah of Masrekah reigned in his stead.

verses.text_plain: And Samlah died, and Saul of Rehoboth by the river reigned in his stead.
verses.verse_html: 37And Samlah died, and Saul of Rehoboth by the river reigned in his stead.

verses.text_plain: And Saul died, and Baal–hanan the son of Achbor reigned in his stead.
verses.verse_html: 38And Saul died, and Baal–hanan the son of Achbor reigned in his stead.

verses.text_plain: And Baal–hanan the son of Achbor died, and Hadar reigned in his stead: and the name of his city was Pau; and his wife’s name was Mehetabel, the daughter of Matred, the daughter of Mezahab.
verses.verse_html:
39And Baal–hanan the son of Achbor died, and Hadar reigned in his stead: and the name of his city was Pau; and his wife’s name was Mehetabel, the daughter of Matred, the daughter of Mezahab. ▼
▼ Hadar, Pau: or, Hadad, Pai: after his death was an Aristocracy

tokens.text: in his stead: and the name

footnotes.body_text: ▼ Hadar, Pau: or, Hadad, Pai: after his death was an Aristocracy
footnotes.body_html: ▼ Hadar, Pau: or, Hadad, Pai: after his death was an Aristocracy

verses.text_plain: And these are the names of the dukes that came of Esau, according to their families, after their places, by their names; duke Timnah, duke Alvah, duke Jetheth,
verses.verse_html:
40And these are the names of the dukes that came of Esau, according to their families, after their places, by their names; duke Timnah, duke Alvah, duke Jetheth, ▼
▼ Alvah: or, Aliah

verses.text_plain: Duke Aholibamah, duke Elah, duke Pinon,
verses.verse_html: 41Duke Aholibamah, duke Elah, duke Pinon,

verses.text_plain: Duke Kenaz, duke Teman, duke Mibzar,
verses.verse_html: 42Duke Kenaz, duke Teman, duke Mibzar,

verses.text_plain: Duke Magdiel, duke Iram: these be the dukes of Edom, according to their habitations in the land of their possession: he is Esau the father of the Edomites.
verses.verse_html:
43Duke Magdiel, duke Iram: these be the dukes of Edom, according to their habitations in the land of their possession: he is Esau the father of the Edomites. ▼
▼ the Edomites: Heb. Edom

footnotes.body_html: ▼ the Edomites: Heb. Edom
